# TerraScope Frontend - Django Web Application

A Django-based web interface for the TerraScope geospatial data management system.

## ğŸ›  Technology Stack

| Component | Technology | Version |
|-----------|-----------|---------|
| **Web Framework** | Django | 4.x+ |
| **Database** | SQLite | 3.x |
| **Frontend** | HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript | - |
| **Charts** | Chart.js | 3.x+ |
| **Template Engine** | Django Templates | Built-in |
| **Static Files** | Django Static Files | Built-in |

